This paper deals with a problem in the domain of mobile robots, which is a subfield of robotics and falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The problem involves coordination and communication among the robots, which suggests that it may also fall under the sub-categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
